1114.name: Cronimo Ti
1114.Applications: Rutile low carbon electrode for welding low-alloyed steel to stainless or austenitic manganese steels, it is suitable for stainless cladding. Weld metal has corrosion resistance to acids and salt water
1114.Suitable_For: NF A 35-578 : Z 15 CN 24.13 ASTM/AISI : 304, 347, 309 DIN 17175 : X 12 CrNi 22.12. Werkstoff Nr : 1.4828, 1.4311, 1.4712, 1.4742. UGINE : NS 24, R 27. All construction steels , low alloyed in combination with stainless steels.
